OL,3,CPair deny historic child sex offences
OL,4,Cat former children's centre
OL,6,FTwo men have denied committing dozens
OL,7,Fof historic child sexual offences at a
OL,8,Fformer children's centre in
OL,9,FAbergavenny.
OL,11,FAngus Riddell, 69, and Robin
OL,12,FGriffiths, 65, appeared before Merthyr
OL,13,FTydfil Crown Court on Friday, charged
OL,14,Fwith 45 offences between them relating
OL,15,Fto 16 victims.
OL,17,FThe alleged sexual and physical
OL,18,Foffences took place predominantly at
OL,19,Fthe Coed Glas Assessment Centre,
OL,20,Fbetween the 1970s and 1990s.
