OL,6,FBoth men appeared in the dock to deny
OL,7,Fthe charges.
OL,9,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, set a date
OL,10,Ffor trial, which is expected to last
OL,11,Fthree months.
OL,13,FShe said: "As you have heard, now that
OL,14,Fyou have pleaded not guilty the trial
OL,15,Fdate has been set.
OL,17,F"You will both be bailed now to your
OL,18,Ftrial date on 18 January, 2027."
